All 7 tests pass and the experiment is complete. The final implementation in `src/game-of-life.ts`:

- **`countNeighbors`** - counts live cells within the Moore neighborhood of a given cell
- **`neighborPositions`** - returns the 8 neighboring positions for a cell (functional style)
- **`isDeadCell`** - checks if a position is unoccupied
- **`deduplicate`** - removes duplicate cells using a coordinate-keyed Map
- **`nextGeneration`** - computes the next generation via survival (2-3 neighbors) + birth (exactly 3 neighbors)

The TDD cycle completed all 7 tests across the full Red-Green-Refactor workflow.
